WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.240
In Moscow this morning,

00:00:01.241 --> 00:00:02.761
Russian President Vladimir Putin

00:00:02.762 --> 00:00:06.121
used the annual celebration of the end of WWII in Europe

00:00:06.122 --> 00:00:08.461
to try to justify the war in Ukraine.

00:00:08.720 --> 00:00:11.280
the VE Day parade featured thousands of soldiers,

00:00:11.281 --> 00:00:13.381
including many who have fought in Ukraine.

00:00:13.400 --> 00:00:17.700
In a speech, Putin said Russia “will not allow anyone” to threaten it.

00:00:17.760 --> 00:00:19.440
According to Russian news agencies,

00:00:19.441 --> 00:00:21.241
Putin also said this morning

00:00:21.242 --> 00:00:24.881
there is nothing unusual in the upcoming military exercise

00:00:24.882 --> 00:00:28.980
to practice the use of tactical nuclear weapons on the battlefield.
